text: 't Haantje may refer to: * 't Haantje, Drenthe, a small village in of Coevorden, Drenthe, Netherlands * 't Haantje, North Brabant, a hamlet in the municipality of Steenbergen, North Brabant, Netherlands * 't Haantje, Overijssel, a hamlet in the municipality of Hardenberg, Overijssel, Netherlands
title: 't Haantje
